{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["expand_udim"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 16], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [97, 155], "text": ["Perform UDIM or UVTILE texture filename expansion."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [221, 344], "text": ["Scans the input path for special conversion characters to perform either UDIM\n    or UVTILE style filename expansion."]}], "indent": 0, "text": [" ", {"text": ["string expand_udim(float u, float v; string path, ...)"], "type": "code"}], "role": "item", "extent": [155, 221], "type": "usage"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "usage_group"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [344, 415], "text": ["This is similar to ", {"text": "", "value": "/vex/functions/texprintf", "fallback_text": "texprintf()", "fullpath": "/vex/functions/texprintf", "scheme": "Vex", "type": "link"}, ", with two significant differences:"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [415, 498], "text": ["There are no variadic print arguments. Only UDIM/UVTILE expansion is performed."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [498, 609], "text": ["If UDIM/UVTILE expansion was performed, the function checks to see if the texture exists and is accessible."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [624, 698], "text": ["The texture coordinates to translate into a UDIM tile specification."]}], "indent": 0, "text": [{"text": ["u"], "type": "code"}, ", ", {"text": ["v"], "type": "code"}], "role": "item", "extent": [609, 624], "type": "arg"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [711, 880], "text": ["A file path. Special character sequences in the path will be expanded into UDIM specifiers based on the given UV coordinates. The special conversion sequences are:"]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "text": [{"text": ["%(UDIM)d"], "type": "code"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [880, 897], "type": "cell"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [897, 976], "text": ["The UDIM coordinate, as computed by ", {"text": ["1000 + int(u)+1 + int(v)*10"], "type": "code"}]}], "role": "td", "type": "cell"}], "divider": false, "type": "row"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "text": [{"text": ["%(U)d"], "type": "code"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [976, 990], "type": "cell"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [990, 1042], "text": ["The UVTILE style u-coordinate (", {"text": ["int(u)+1"], "type": "code"}, ")"]}], "role": "td", "type": "cell"}], "divider": false, "type": "row"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "text": [{"text": ["%(V)d"], "type": "code"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [1042, 1056], "type": "cell"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1056, 1108], "text": ["The UVTILE style v-coordinate (", {"text": ["int(v)+1"], "type": "code"}, ")"]}], "role": "td", "type": "cell"}], "divider": false, "type": "row"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "text": [{"text": ["%(UVTILE)d"], "type": "code"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [1108, 1127], "type": "cell"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1127, 1192], "text": ["Expands both u and v coordinates in the form ", {"text": ["u%d_v%d"], "type": "code"}, "."]}], "role": "td", "type": "cell"}], "divider": false, "type": "row"}], "type": "table", "thead": []}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1192, 1332], "text": ["The ", {"text": ["d"], "type": "code"}, " conversion specifier for texture identification can be modified with\n    field modifiers.  For example ", {"text": ["%(U)02d"], "type": "code"}, " or ", {"text": ["%(V)04d"], "type": "code"}, "."]}], "indent": 0, "text": [{"text": ["path"], "type": "code"}], "role": "item", "extent": [698, 711], "type": "arg"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1381, 1547], "text": ["Normally, the function checks whether the expanded path exists and is readable. If you pass the ", {"text": ["\"checkfile\", 0"], "type": "code"}, " pair, the function will not perform this check."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["checkfile"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"default": "1", "type": "int"}, "extent": [1332, 1349], "variadic": true, "type": "arg"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1557, 1617], "text": ["The path with any UDIM control sequences replaced."]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1617, 1781], "text": ["If the expanded file path does not exist or is not readable, the function will return an empty string, unless you turn off the ", {"text": ["checkfile"], "type": "code"}, " variadic argument."]}], "indent": 0, "returns": true, "role": "item", "extent": [1547, 1557], "type": "arg"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "arg_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1791, 1865], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.1, 4.15, \"map_%(UDIM)d.rat\")"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"map_1044.rat\""]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1865, 1946], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.1, 4.15, \"map_%(U)02d_%(V)02d.rat\")"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"map_04_05.rat\""]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1946, 2027], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.14, 11.5, \"map_u%(U)d_v%(V)d.rat\")"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"map_u4_v12.rat\""]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2027, 2116], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.14, 11.5, \"missing_file%(UDIM)d.rat\")"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"\" for missing files."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2116, 2253], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.14, 11.5, \"missing_file%(UDIM)d.rat\", \"checkfile\", 0)"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"missing_file1044.rat\" since \"checkfile\" is disabled."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2253, 2401], "text": [{"text": ["expand_udim(3.14, 11.5, \"/path/file.rat\")"], "type": "code"}, " - Returns \"/path/file.rat\" whether the file exists or not since there are no UDIM/UVTILE expansions."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}, {"lang": "vex", "indent": 0, "type": "pre", "extent": [2401, 2699], "text": ["\n\n// sprintf() will leave the %(UDIM)d format sequence unmodified.\nstring map = sprintf(\"%s/%s_%(UDIM)d.rat\", texture_path, texture_base);\n// Expand the %(UDIM)d, returning an empty string if the map doesn't exist.\nmap = expand_udim(u, v, map);\nif (map != \"\")\nCf = texture(map, u, v);\n"]}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Examples", "role": "section", "extent": [1781, 1791], "container": true, "type": "examples_section", "id": "examples"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2710, 2728], "text": [{"text": "", "value": "/vex/functions/texprintf", "fallback_text": "texprintf()", "fullpath": "/vex/functions/texprintf", "scheme": "Vex", "type": "link"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2728, 2744], "text": [{"text": "", "value": "/vex/functions/texture", "fallback_text": "texture()", "fullpath": "/vex/functions/texture", "scheme": "Vex", "type": "link"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [2699, 2710], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Perform UDIM or UVTILE texture filename expansion."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"showtags": "true", "group": "texture", "type": "vex", "context": "all", "tags": "utility, texture, string, udim"}, "title": ["expand_udim"]}